title: Winners And Losers - S03E26 - Must Come To A End.avi
description:
Winners And Losers - S03E26 - Must Come To A End

Bec and Ryan attend a farewell party and then begin their new lives together. Carla and Doug decide they want to have a baby together and she stops taking her meds. Sam and Adam get married only hours before he dies in her arms. Flynn confesses his love for Sam and moves to New Zealand indefinitely. Rhys returns and asks Jonathan to move to America with him. Sophie has trouble dealing with her crush on Luke. Gabe tells Jenny that he wants to be with her. Frances is made a partner of the law firm and discovers she's five weeks pregnant.
